  <entry>
    <title>使用hexo搭建blog(二)</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/12/19/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAblog(%E4%BA%8C)/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/12/19/使用hexo搭建blog(二)/</id>
    <published>2017-12-19T15:30:29.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-12-23T11:48:07.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用<a href="http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">不蒜子</a>就是统计站点的总访问量，即统计浏览了多少次；有多少人访问</p><h2 id="不蒜子配置及使用"><a href="#不蒜子配置及使用" class="headerlink" title="不蒜子配置及使用"></a>不蒜子配置及使用</h2><p>1、在主题目录下 themes/next/layout/_partials目录下的footer.swig文件<br>2、在文件末尾插入以下代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script async src=&quot;https://dn-lbstatics.qbox.me/busuanzi/2.3/busuanzi.pure.mini.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">本站总访问量 &lt;span id=&quot;busuanzi_value_site_pv&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 次&amp;nbsp&amp;nbsp&amp;nbsp</span><br><span class="line">本站访客数&lt;span id=&quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;人次</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加站内搜索"><a href="#添加站内搜索" class="headerlink" title="添加站内搜索"></a>添加站内搜索</h2><p>1、添加依赖</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br><span class="line">2、_config.yml内容：</span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # if auto, trigger search by changing input</span><br><span class="line">  # if manual, trigger search by pressing enter key or search button</span><br><span class="line">  trigger: auto</span><br><span class="line">  # show top n results per article, show all results by setting to -1</span><br><span class="line">  top_n_per_article: 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2、在主题目录下 themes/next/_config.yml</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true //默认为false</span><br><span class="line">  # if auto, trigger search by changing input</span><br><span class="line">  # if manual, trigger search by pressing enter key or search button</span><br><span class="line">  trigger: auto</span><br><span class="line">  # show top n results per article, show all results by setting to -1</span><br><span class="line">  top_n_per_article: 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加打赏功能"><a href="#添加打赏功能" class="headerlink" title="添加打赏功能"></a>添加打赏功能</h2><p>1、获取微信二维码和支付宝二维码,具体做法就是先保存二维码到相册，再编辑照片裁剪出二维码图片（笨笨的方法）</p><p>2、将准备的二维码照片放在themes/next/source/images/</p><p>3、在主题目录themes/next/_config.yml放开以下代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reward_comment: 不要脸了~ _ ~不要脸了</span><br><span class="line">wechatpay: /images/webchatpay.jpg</span><br><span class="line">alipay: /images/alipay.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新构建就可以看到打赏效果了。</p><p><font color="#d9b100">本人觉得打赏那个抖动效果不好，想直接去掉了，可以使用以下操作</font>：</p><p>修改next/source/css/_common/components/post/post-reward.styl文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/* 注释文字闪动效果</span><br><span class="line">#wechat:hover p&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    animation: roll 0.1s infinite linear;</span><br><span class="line">    -webkit-animation: roll 0.1s infinite linear;</span><br><span class="line">    -moz-animation: roll 0.1s infinite linear;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#alipay:hover p&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    animation: roll 0.1s infinite linear;</span><br><span class="line">    -webkit-animation: roll 0.1s infinite linear;</span><br><span class="line">    -moz-animation: roll 0.1s infinite linear;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">*/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加评论"><a href="#添加评论" class="headerlink" title="添加评论"></a>添加评论</h2><p>next支持不少评论插件，以下都是可以内部支持的</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;duoshuo.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;disqus.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;hypercomments.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;youyan.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;livere.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;changyan.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;gitment.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% include &apos;valine.swig&apos; %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本人使用的是livere(使用了一个简单点的·来必力)</p><p>1、到<a href="https://livere.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">来必力</a>注册账号，填写站点</p><p><img src="../../../../../images/20171220/201712203.png" alt="&quot;图片描述&quot;"></p><p>2、拿到uid</p><p><img src="../../../../../images/20171220/201712204.png" alt="&quot;图片描述&quot;"></p><p>3、在主题目录themes/next/_config.yml放开以下代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Support for LiveRe comments system.</span><br><span class="line"># You can get your uid from https://livere.com/insight/myCode (General web site)</span><br><span class="line"># 来必力</span><br><span class="line">livere_uid: youruid</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;使用&lt;a href=&quot;http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;不蒜子&lt;/a&gt;就是统计站点的总访问量，即统计浏览了多少次；有多少人访问&lt;/p&gt;
