    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用以下命令前需要安装node环境，可以自行百度</p><h2 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo npm install -g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="初始化项目blog"><a href="#初始化项目blog" class="headerlink" title="初始化项目blog"></a>初始化项目blog</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 建立一个博客文件夹blog</span><br><span class="line">$ cd blog</span><br><span class="line">// 并初始化博客</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo --save</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-server --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建新文章"><a href="#创建新文章" class="headerlink" title="创建新文章"></a>创建新文章</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new mac下使用hexo搭建blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="生成静态页面"><a href="#生成静态页面" class="headerlink" title="生成静态页面"></a>生成静态页面</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate  // 简写 hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="本地预览"><a href="#本地预览" class="headerlink" title="本地预览"></a>本地预览</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server  // 简写 hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="设置主题Theme"><a href="#设置主题Theme" class="headerlink" title="设置主题Theme"></a>设置主题Theme</h2><p>可以到官方提供的主题列表中选取</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ cd themes/</span><br><span class="line">$ git clone git@github.com:iissnan/hexo-theme-next.git themes/next</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">_config.yml配置文件中设置：</span><br><span class="line">theme: next</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/iNerdStack/inerdstack.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>_config.yml配置文件中设置</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/iNerdStack/inerdstack.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="blog提交"><a href="#blog提交" class="headerlink" title="blog提交"></a>blog提交</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo generate   </span><br><span class="line">// hexo d</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建分类、tag等"><a href="#创建分类、tag等" class="headerlink" title="创建分类、tag等"></a>创建分类、tag等</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 添加分类页面</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new page &quot;categories&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加阅读数"><a href="#添加阅读数" class="headerlink" title="添加阅读数"></a>添加阅读数</h2><p>配置LeanCloud</p><p>1、打开<a href="https://leancloud.cn/dashboard/applist.html#/apps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LeanCloud</a>官网，注册一个账号，完成激活 </p><p>2、创建应用</p><p><img src="../../../../../images/20171218/201712184.png" alt="&quot;图片描述&quot;"> </p><p>3、点击创建Class，类名叫做Counter</p><p><img src="../../../../../images/20171218/201712181.png" alt="&quot;图片描述&quot;"> </p><p>4、修改主题配置文件_config.yml</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Show number of visitors to each article.</span><br><span class="line"># You can visit https://leancloud.cn get AppID and AppKey.</span><br><span class="line">leancloud_visitors:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  app_id: xx_id</span><br><span class="line">  app_key: xx_key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="../../../../../images/20171218/201712182.png" alt="&quot;图片描述&quot;"> </p><p>配置域名</p><p><img src="../../../../../images/20171218/201712183.png" alt="&quot;图片描述&quot;"> </p>]]></content>
    
